---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Blog - Neon Injector"
  description="Stay updated with the latest news, tips, and updates about Neon Injector, your go-to tool for Mobile Legends skin customization."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex-1 pt-16">
      <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--text-color)]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neon-purple mb-8 text-center">Neon Injector Blog</h1>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="mb-6">Welcome to the Neon Injector Blog! Here, we share the latest news, updates, tips, and community highlights to help you get the most out of your Mobile Legends skin customization experience. Our blog is your go-to resource for staying informed about new features, troubleshooting guides, and best practices for using Neon Injector safely and effectively.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Latest Posts</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Check out our recent posts below for insights, updates, and tutorials. Join our <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord community</a> to discuss these topics and share your own tips!</p>

          <article class="mb-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neon-purple mb-3">Neon Injector v2.3.1: Faster Injections and New Skins</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Posted on August 1, 2025</p>
            <p class="mb-4">We’re thrilled to announce Neon Injector v2.3.1, our latest release packed with performance improvements and an expanded skin library. This update reduces injection times by up to 30%, supports the latest Mobile Legends patch, and introduces new skins for heroes like Alucard, Miya, and Gusion. Learn how to update your app and explore the new skins in our <a href="/docs" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Documentation</a>.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">Key highlights of v2.3.1:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li>Optimized SAF and Shizuku integration for smoother performance.</li>
              <li>New skins added, including exclusive Epic and Legendary designs.</li>
              <li>Improved error handling for failed injections with detailed feedback.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Have questions about the update? Reach out via our <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a> or join our <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord server</a> for real-time support.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="mb-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neon-purple mb-3">Top 5 Tips for Safe Skin Customization</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Posted on July 15, 2025</p>
            <p class="mb-4">Using Neon Injector to customize Mobile Legends skins is fun and rewarding, but it’s important to do so safely. Here are our top five tips to ensure a secure and enjoyable experience:</p>
            <ul class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Use a Secondary Account</strong>: Protect your main Mobile Legends account by testing skins on a secondary account to avoid potential bans.</li>
              <li><strong>Download from Official Sources</strong>: Always get Neon Injector from our official website to avoid malicious versions.</li>
              <li><strong>Keep Your App Updated</strong>: Regularly check for updates in the app’s <strong>Settings > Check for Updates</strong> to stay compatible with Mobile Legends patches.</li>
              <li><strong>Follow Setup Guides</strong>: Refer to our <a href="/docs" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Documentation</a> for proper SAF or Shizuku setup.</li>
              <li><strong>Join the Community</strong>: Engage with other users on our <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord server</a> to share tips and get help.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Read more about safe usage in our <a href="/disclaimer" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Disclaimer</a> or contact us at <a href="mailto:support@neon-injector.my.id" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a> for personalized assistance.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="mb-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neon-purple mb-3">Community Spotlight: Your Favorite Skins</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Posted on June 30, 2025</p>
            <p class="mb-4">Our community has been sharing their favorite Neon Injector skins on Discord, and we’re excited to highlight some of the most popular picks! From Alucard’s fiery “Obsidian Blade” to Miya’s elegant “Moonlight Archer,” our skin library offers something for every player. Here’s what our community loves:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li><strong>Alucard - Obsidian Blade</strong>: A fan-favorite for its sleek design and vibrant effects.</li>
              <li><strong>Miya - Moonlight Archer</strong>: Perfect for players who love a mystical aesthetic.</li>
              <li><strong>Gusion - Cosmic Gleam</strong>: A standout choice for its futuristic look.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Want to share your favorite skin? Join our <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord server</a> and post in the #skin-showcase channel. Stay tuned for more community spotlights and skin library updates!</p>
          </article>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">Stay Connected</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">Our blog is updated regularly with new posts about Neon Injector features, Mobile Legends tips, and community events. Subscribe to our newsletter or join our <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord server</a> to stay in the loop. For questions or support, visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a> or email us at <a href="mailto:support@neon-injector.my.id" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>